         <abstract id="aspace_382eec8eb45afdaef58d08765d78940d">The papers contain legal documents, correspondence, and miscellaneous papers primarily concerned with Gaston-François-Christophe de Lévis, duc de Ventadour (1794-1863). The papers, in French, primarily relate to inheritance of land in Martinique.</abstract>
